Every Flavor Generator

During a d20 game, another player asked me what my potion tasted like. I immediately thought of Bertie Bott's Every Flavor Beans, from JK Rowling's Harry Potter series, and went to the internet to find such a generator of flavors. To my surprise, there was none, so I wrote this.

